OL,5, Esther Ghey and Ian Russell greet each 
OL,6, other with a hug. The pair have a lot  
OL,7, in common - though they would surely   
OL,8, prefer that they had never had cause to
OL,9, meet.                                  
OL,11,F"So good to meet you," says Esther, as 
OL,12,FIan smiles warmly.                     
OL,14,FBoth parents have been bereaved in     
OL,15,Fshocking and very public circumstances.
OL,17,FIan lost his 14-year-old daughter Molly
OL,18,Fafter she took her own life six years  
OL,19,Fago, and Esther's daughter Brianna, who
OL,20,Fwas transgender, was murdered one year 
OL,21,Fago this week.                         
